messageBody:
Hi!
We have been testing a snapshot for the last week and it seems pretty stable. No bugs so far. Problem is: we are going to release soon and we need to decide if we roll back to 4.11.
Can anyone tell me if theres any concrete plans for a 4.12 release?
Regards!
